# Contact FundingCompass

---

## Editorial Team

For corrections, factual disputes, or content feedback:

**Email:** [hello@fundingcompass.guide](mailto:hello@fundingcompass.guide)

We read every message and respond to factual corrections within 5 business days. If you believe a rate, qualification requirement, or product description on this site is incorrect, include the specific claim, the page URL, and a source for the correct information.

---

## Partnership and Advertising Enquiries

For affiliate partnership, advertising, or sponsored content discussions:

**Email:** [hello@fundingcompass.guide](mailto:hello@fundingcompass.guide) with subject line: Partnership Enquiry

Please review our [Editorial Standards](/editorial-standards/) and [How We Make Money](/how-we-make-money/) pages before reaching out — they explain what commercial relationships we will and will not accept.

