## Response Times

| Enquiry type | Expected response |
|---|---|
| Factual corrections | 5 business days |
| General editorial questions | 5–10 business days |
| Partnership enquiries | 5–10 business days |
| Press / media requests | 5 business days |

We do not respond to requests that ask us to modify editorial content in exchange for payment, link exchanges, or other commercial arrangements not disclosed in our [editorial standards](/editorial-standards/).
